{"code":0,"data":[{"cid":598528,"deleted":false,"image_metadata":{},"is_dz":false,"name":"Alice","permissions":["report"],"pid":124317,"reply_to":-1,"tag":null,"text":"抱抱dz","timestamp":1606034969,"type":"text","url":""},{"cid":598535,"deleted":false,"image_metadata":{},"is_dz":false,"name":"Bob","permissions":["report"],"pid":124317,"reply_to":-1,"tag":null,"text":"我也是","timestamp":1606035041,"type":"text","url":""},{"cid":598536,"deleted":false,"image_metadata":{},"is_dz":false,"name":"Carol","permissions":["report"],"pid":124317,"reply_to":-1,"tag":null,"text":"抱抱，多享受享受挺好的，累了就摸摸鱼，来劲儿就多干点，都会变好的","timestamp":1606035072,"type":"text","url":""},{"cid":598541,"deleted":false,"image_metadata":{},"is_dz":false,"name":"Dave","permissions":["report"],"pid":124317,"reply_to":-1,"tag":null,"text":"cz的想法和dz差不多，cz最好的朋友今年上半年离世了，当时也想了很多，patpatdz","timestamp":1606035117,"type":"text","url":""},{"cid":598545,"deleted":false,"image_metadata":{},"is_dz":true,"name":"洞主","permissions":["report"],"pid":124317,"reply_to":-1,"tag":null,"text":"Re Bob: 有类似经验的人可以share一下自己的心路历程吗？我不确定自己的这种状态对不对 或者是否需要调整","timestamp":1606035134,"type":"text","url":""},{"cid":598547,"deleted":false,"image_metadata":{},"is_dz":false,"name":"Eve","permissions":["report"],"pid":124317,"reply_to":-1,"tag":null,"text":"抱抱dz，dave最近也遇到了跟你相似的情况，只能说珍惜眼前人叭…","timestamp":1606035155,"type":"text","url":""},{"cid":598566,"deleted":false,"image_metadata":{},"is_dz":false,"name":"Francis","permissions":["report"],"pid":124317,"reply_to":-1,"tag":null,"text":"cz没有经历过这种事情但有相同的心境，可能是父母从小潜移默化传达给我的吧","timestamp":1606035386,"type":"text","url":""},{"cid":598569,"deleted":false,"image_metadata":{},"is_dz":false,"name":"Dave","permissions":["report"],"pid":124317,"reply_to":-1,"tag":null,"text":"Re 洞主: 不需要，虽然这样说可能对逝者有些许冒犯，但cz还是要说，时间会淡化一切。当时cz就是，前几天伤心欲绝，后来慢慢恢复到以前的状态了，只是没有像以前那样关注成绩、得失、输赢了。","timestamp":1606035644,"type":"text","url":""},{"cid":598579,"deleted":false,"image_metadata":{},"is_dz":true,"name":"洞主","permissions":["report"],"pid":124317,"reply_to":-1,"tag":null,"text":"Re Dave: 如果Dave不介意 可以分享一下自己当时的心路历程吗？ （如果不太方便在这里分享，可以匿名写邮件吗）","timestamp":1606035865,"type":"text","url":""},{"cid":598659,"deleted":false,"image_metadata":{},"is_dz":false,"name":"Grace","permissions":["report"],"pid":124317,"reply_to":-1,"tag":null,"text":"Re 洞主: 是对的。早晚要遇到的事情，只不过总会有我们这样不幸的人，也被迫更早去想清楚","timestamp":1606037362,"type":"text","url":""},{"cid":598742,"deleted":false,"image_metadata":{},"is_dz":false,"name":"Hans","permissions":["report"],"pid":124317,"reply_to":-1,"tag":null,"text":"读懂悲剧让我们更加热爱生活\n见过死亡让我们更加珍惜生命\ndz加油呀","timestamp":1606038822,"type":"text","url":""},{"cid":599137,"deleted":false,"image_metadata":{},"is_dz":false,"name":"Isabella","permissions":["report"],"pid":124317,"reply_to":-1,"tag":null,"text":"dz加油，慢慢走","timestamp":1606044549,"type":"text","url":""},{"cid":599169,"deleted":false,"image_metadata":{},"is_dz":false,"name":"Jason","permissions":["report"],"pid":124317,"reply_to":-1,"tag":null,"text":"Re 洞主: 拍拍dz，我和你很像。cz的爸爸在cz高三那年查出癌症晚期，没等到我高考就走了。爸爸刚走的那段时间我经常半夜心口痛，做噩梦；也会常常出神，无数次想起见到爸爸的最后一面，无数次想起他瘦到脱形后冰冷的眼睛。cz当时觉得痛到呼吸都费力，就去拼命学习麻痹自己。直到大概一年后cz状态开始慢慢好起来，突然就明白了很多事没必要争争抢抢。除了生死，哪件不是小事","timestamp":1606044940,"type":"text","url":""},{"cid":599172,"deleted":false,"image_metadata":{},"is_dz":false,"name":"Kate","permissions":["report"],"pid":124317,"reply_to":-1,"tag":null,"text":"cz的心态也是这样，失去了至亲以后佛系了很多…更加享受现在，更加珍惜眼前人。","timestamp":1606044991,"type":"text","url":""},{"cid":599174,"deleted":false,"image_metadata":{},"is_dz":false,"name":"Jason","permissions":["report"],"pid":124317,"reply_to":-1,"tag":null,"text":"世间好物不坚牢，彩云易散琉璃脆。","timestamp":1606045026,"type":"text","url":""},{"cid":599185,"deleted":false,"image_metadata":{},"is_dz":false,"name":"Jason","permissions":["report"],"pid":124317,"reply_to":-1,"tag":null,"text":"好好珍惜当下，好好活着，好好享受眼前的快乐和痛苦。","timestamp":1606045120,"type":"text","url":""},{"cid":599974,"deleted":false,"image_metadata":{},"is_dz":true,"name":"洞主","permissions":["report"],"pid":124317,"reply_to":-1,"tag":null,"text":"Re Jason: 是的\n","timestamp":1606057310,"type":"text","url":""},{"cid":606127,"deleted":false,"image_metadata":{},"is_dz":false,"name":"Louis","permissions":["report"],"pid":124317,"reply_to":-1,"tag":null,"text":"拍拍你，享受生活就好了","timestamp":1606190765,"type":"text","url":""},{"cid":606655,"deleted":false,"image_metadata":{},"is_dz":false,"name":"Margaret","permissions":["report"],"pid":124317,"reply_to":-1,"tag":null,"text":"习惯就好","timestamp":1606197324,"type":"text","url":""},{"cid":2342095,"deleted":false,"image_metadata":{},"is_dz":false,"name":"Grace","permissions":["report"],"pid":124317,"reply_to":-1,"tag":null,"text":" ","timestamp":1629727051,"type":"text","url":""}],"post":{"attention":false,"deleted":false,"image_metadata":{},"likenum":23,"permissions":["report","fold"],"pid":124317,"reply":20,"tag":null,"text":"至亲去世后对我最大的影响是：意识到周围存在的一切都是短暂的，人世无常。在更加珍惜的同时，也少了一些执念。不像以前那样奋力拼命去追求一些名和利，而是更加珍惜、享受生活。本来可能会一周七天地拼命学习和research，现在意识到人也只能活几十年且可能存在意外，会抽出一些时间去旅游、享受美食，做自己爱做的事。 \n\n这是变得更加平凡了吗？是更佛了吗？我不知道。或许有一天我会走出来，或许我还会成为原来的那个我？让时间来说明一切吧。","timestamp":1606034834,"type":"text","updated_at":1629727052,"url":"","vote":{}}}